706959f.title: Brooklyn: Surf Ave. - Jones Walk
706959f.text:
Surf Ave., (rear view), south side, between Jones Walk and West 10th Street. This is a view of Feltwan's Restaurant, pavilion apd bathhouse, showing a part of the Beach and Surf Ave., in the early 1870'.
About 1875.
Eugene L. Arwbruster Colleetion.
